title: Tig Notaro
itunes:title: Tig Notaro
itunes:subtitle: TIG NOTARO (Boyish Girl Interrupted, One Mississippi, Transparent, Happy to Be Here) joins Anna to discuss high school, delivering pizza, a three-year-old’s wisdom, self-diagnosed prosopagnosia, Taylor Dayne and the progression of a comedy career. Anna an
description:
In this episode...

- Talk show expectations
- High school drop out to comedy star
- Delivering pizza
- The secret language of twins
- A life changing moment at the coffee shop
- A three-year-old’s wisdom
- Self-diagnosed prosopagnosia
- Taylor Dayne
- Silly nonsense and cancer
- From one-liners to a 14-minute joke
- Tig’s cat’s Instagram
- Burritos
- Advice to callers Abby and Jerry
